    },
    {
        "en": "I shall perform meritorious deeds at the proper times, failing not in my efficacy and faith. As the talisman burns, my body offers its gratitude to the Supreme Yin.",
        "cn": "当以时言功，不负效信，随箓焚化，身谢太阴。",
        "pinyin": "Dāng yǐ shí yán gōng, bù fù xiào xìn, suí lù fénhuà, shēn xiè Tàiyīn.",
        "type": "Technique/Art/Method/Incantation/Spell",
        "gender": null,
        "file": 8
    },
    {
        "en": "to govern my destiny and soothe my spirit, as I dedicate myself to pursuing the Dao.",
        "cn": "司命安神，奉道修行。",
        "pinyin": "Sīmìng ānshén, fèngdào xiūxíng.",
